name: Switching Coasts
description:
Yesterday was great, and we got to bed nice and early, which made for an early rollout this morning. We didn't see much traffic along the Eastern Shore (as I've learned it is called), and tried to get as much riding in as possible before the heat got too intense. We were unsuccessful and the heat got intense - over 30 for a couple of hours, with a lot of humidity.

This evening we're camping outside Antigonish. The campus there is impressive, especially for a town of 5000 or so.
